message:
Make concurrency module have no productFlavors

The behavior customization is now done through a resource
app developers can override if they want to report failed checks
without crashing using Timber, or if they want to completely ignore them.

This allow for easier, conflict-less reuse-ability across libraries.

message:
Fix crash below Android 5.0  caused by partial tint support

The root cause is that android:tint doesn't support color resources but
only hardcoded color values prior to Android 5.0.

This commit also disables vector support library for better performance
while scrolling
